description: Jake’s Old Fashioned Ice Cream is truckin’ their delicious old fashioned ice cream through the streets of Nashua, and locals just love to nosh on this dreamily sweet treat. This truck is serving up a succulent selection of super-premium flavors; Cookies-n-Cream, Dulce de Leche, Cheesecake, Coffee Lover, Black Raspberry, S’mores, and Maple Walnut Bacon are just a few that you’ll find. You can even use any of these flavors to make a Jake’s Sundae your own way. So if you see Jake’s Ice Cream at a curb near you, it’s certainly worth hitting the brakes. And if you desire your next party to be a sweet time for everyone, then you should certainly invite Jake’s.
name: Jake's Old Fashioned Ice Cream
